    Get cup results

    get_cup_results.Rd

    Get past or current standings in a Cup.

    Usage

    get_cup_results(cup_id)

    Arguments

    cup_id

    Character. Cup identifier. Find it by calling get_cups().

    Value

    A data.frame. Listing the standings for the queried cup.

    Examples

    get_cup_results("BT2122SWRLCP__SWTS")
